Creating database (catered for example CRUD)
1) phpmyadmin -> Database -> created Database -> #name
2) enter table name and columns. Example is posts / 7 -> go
3) col_1 /  id -> make sure A_I (auto increment is checked) & the primary key
col_2 / title -> VARCHAR / 255 length
col_3 / text -> TEXT / 
col_4 / create_date -> DATETIME  / Default = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
        --SAVE--
